Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.87,0:00:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西岚的遗产…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.29,0:02:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}Weak square
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快走 你们这群人民公敌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.89,0:02:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们出卖祖国中饱私囊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻挠我等的神圣之战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃叛乱者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们抢夺来的财富
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让无数良田播满种子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.28,0:02:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他们已承担了应有的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界将知晓我们的决心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的前方没有迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颗星球的所有土地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将重返我等之手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我军将勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝圣湖——Grand Lake北部进发
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今仍被格拉齐埃斯的归还民们抢占的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那片阔别已久的故乡土地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:02:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的子民们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣光同在 奥古斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是场精彩的演讲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微歇息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.45,0:03:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多人死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我的… 错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.04,0:03:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥古斯塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.75,0:03:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因… 因为我是个孩子 靠不住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝非奥古斯塔您的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是因为自己的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本是应该保护他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本是应该让他们信任我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像母后那样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必将实现您的志向
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各地的反抗已基本停息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从投降领地回收资金的工作也已顺利展开了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.14,0:04:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是托阿德斯最强之矛进军神速的福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已无后顾之忧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅有的那点顾虑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近期也将处理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于可以向下一步进发了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Lake南岸已基本镇压完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要将战线北移
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式开始夺回Grand Lake北岸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库玛里 阿尔西亚 塞维芙尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个地区的几个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应能一举拿下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦桑特的事前工作也起作用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大的障碍 还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉齐埃斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:05:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦当然会将战线向Grand Lake的北部转移
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样一来 碰到的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉齐埃斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会发生正面冲突吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是建国后一直贯彻完全孤立主义的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对联邦袭击其他国家毫不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而如果自己的领地被占
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就另当别论了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某种意义上说 比联邦更加棘手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不接受任何谈判
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要踏入他们的领土
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻就会攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的敌人就是朋友这种想法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不适用于他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们如何行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将左右我们的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能期待文森特的外交能力了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先调查调查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变航路 前往格拉齐埃斯国境
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是跟泰迪学的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有害虫和细菌虎视眈眈贵国的领土
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.67,0:06:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要大意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是… 是！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这可是好机会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意吃相 法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿德斯确实通过这次肃清变强了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.73,0:06:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这也正是我们的大好时机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被肃清的贵族领地内的战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正被移往阿德斯联邦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面最出众的就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从北部菲尔兹领来的舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半年前刚刚新造的船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共八艘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八艘？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离约好的数目不是还剩一艘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但法姆她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后要华丽的谢幕嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次弄来八艘的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你猜那位舰长会露出什么表情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实很值得期待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连米莉亚公主都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.11,0:07:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她承认我们的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经读完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,环Grand Lake条约中关于信号灯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及信号弹的概要都读了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 受益匪浅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不需要我继续指导了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后 挑感兴趣的地方慢慢读吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 差不多可以告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅凭一艘战舰击退阿德斯联邦舰队的方法了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.83,0:07:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是跟你说过没有那种东西了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗拼的是资源
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:07:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉泽尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战要用到的资料？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有些地方不放心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是你 法姆也该稍微学学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆她… 那样就行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是法姆的领航员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次绝对不能失败
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后对上阿德斯会更加艰难
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会那么简单的猎到鲸了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉泽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再稍微借我些力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会用好法姆给的舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺回图兰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时实现你们的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Bird
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 要比赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Race预选赛 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.73,0:09:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就能集齐约好的15艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来你怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不用再待在西尔维厄斯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以回卡尔塔法尔了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有点担心阿黛尔和鲁涅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲莉希特也还不太能帮上妈妈忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在天上便一无是处
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 法姆你难道不想见弗里茨他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想见我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.22,0:09:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗里茨 海涅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.39,0:09:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰也来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你能从死神西尔维厄斯逃出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只傻鸭子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿塔莫拉可生气咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿塔莫拉 这下放心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 是来接我们的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲸鱼 很快就会来一个大猎物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿德斯的移送战舰？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆你们的目标也一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这次会是场激战哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茨维贝尔 维尔茨 卡洛提
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连丘尔维斯和修瓦尔希尔也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 激动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 那可是我们的猎物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻鸭子就退开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆 注意峡谷吹来的气流
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲸鱼 我的鲸鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最佳位置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是吉泽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一叉 归我了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查甘拉特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿德斯第三舰队？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方距离2000
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空族的空中船坞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量小型机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来晚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是阿德斯舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尔等反抗我们 不断抢夺我们的舰只
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在要向尔等挥下复仇之槌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备对空战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,违抗奥古斯塔大义的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要将其轰得粉碎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣光同在 奥古斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.77,0:12:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速射管制装置 启动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一第二联动高射炮开始运转
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该察觉到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.45,0:13:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被阿德斯算计了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有退路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羊入虎口了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 该逃去哪里 吉泽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.69,0:13:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三舰队 查甘拉特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野战机动部队 只有第一到第四编队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有出动全部主力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是长距离型的战列舰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要任务是舰队间的正面对决
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.08,0:13:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话…！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下方的炮塔跟不上Vespa的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞到舰队的下面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贴着海面穿过峡谷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下方联动高射炮 射击！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射击！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么下面也有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终究是空族
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来没有格拉齐埃斯火箭战斗机那种速度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么没劲 新兵器连测试数据都收不上来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科雷修 没有无意义的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 是我失言了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉泽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤离修理甲板 赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿塔莫拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸… 爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 爸爸他…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉泽 冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中弹的是修理甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这损伤不至于坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿塔莫拉不会就那样坠毁的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是最清楚不过的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Bird…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆 那边会被风…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Bird告诉我路了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气流会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冰川落下产生冲击波的那一瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的 法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Bird就穿过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时机…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有一瞬 但一定有能穿过去的时机！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算Grand Bird穿过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们来不及的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须由我们主动生成改变气流的冲击波
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆的信号弹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸引火力？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只傻鸭子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就朝我们开火了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认到法姆机的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吸引第三舰队火力的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟随我们的诱导
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:16:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往峡谷的深处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,协助她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.13,0:17:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路顺风！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肆意妄为的丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空族方一起逃向峡谷深处了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.05,0:17:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数据收集基本完成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该结果他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮发射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就现在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生阵风卷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎开到最大 开启备用电路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去追空族
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.57,0:18:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可… 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大群Grand Bird挡住视线 无法捕捉到空族
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.31,0:18:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.15,0:19:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们混乱移民团 就这个优点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于前段时间肃清归还民…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.66,0:19:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么突然太失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.12,0:19:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想阁下的立场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非… 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也难怪你们会不安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 什么都不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们混乱地区人民的忠诚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥古斯塔清楚得很
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 说的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 这是当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真是胆小鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被打得很惨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后会怎样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:19:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不过是以捕鲸为生而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 就算那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.22,0:20:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是徒劳一场
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆 我们也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 吉泽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我发一下消息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.36,0:20:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗 让她们走掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵守约定 是空族的荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此任性十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.37,0:20:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但请再让我们胡闹一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为米莉亚还在等着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.47,0:20:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要再找新的猎物就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能这样平安回来 多亏了吉泽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.48,0:21:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和吉泽在一起的话 肯定没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vespa接近 是法姆机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆机返航
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.87,0:21:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开停泊舱口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去接她们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 您走好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆机后方 距离05
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多个引擎音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:21:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被跟踪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.87,0:21:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安夏尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.50,0:22:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.93,0:22:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到来自第一舰队总司令官萨德里元帅的通信信号
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.76,0:22:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出米莉亚公主
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击沉贵舰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
